    <!-- About Screen -->
    <string name="about_title">About PitchApp</string>
    <string name="about_motivation_text">A tribute to the legendary PitchLab Lite. For years, PitchLab was the go-to tuning app for musicians, loved for its strobe visuals and unparalleled accuracy. Unfortunately, it lost support and became incompatible with modern Android devices.\n\nPitchApp was born to fill that void. Our main goal is to provide a highly functional, simple, and accurate instrument tuner that is, above all, completely free of ads and distractions.</string>
